OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772041214
OL,3,CChef to take 'bile duct cancer' fight
OL,4,Cto Westminster after wife's tragic
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA Worthing chef who adapted his career
OL,8,Fto life as a single father is heading
OL,9,Fto the House of Commons to demand
OL,10,Furgent changes to liver cancer care.
OL,12,FAaron Dalton, whose wife Sally died
OL,13,Ffrom cholangiocarcinoma`an aggressive
OL,14,Fbile duct cancer`just one year after
OL,15,Fher diagnosis, is joining forces with
OL,16,Fthe charity AMMF to highlight a
OL,17,F"treatment lottery."
OL,19,FNew NHS data reveals 67% of patients
OL,20,Fdiagnosed with the disease receive no
OL,21,Fcancer-specific treatment at all.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
