FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772041214
OL,3,CChef to take 'bile duct cancer' fight
OL,4,Cto Westminster after wife's tragic
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FSally, a dedicated paediatric nurse,
OL,8,Fdiscovered the cancer by chance while
OL,9,Fundergoing tests for a different
OL,10,Fsurgery. Aaron describes the moment
OL,11,Ftheir world "imploded" when a scan
OL,12,Frevealed a shadow on her liver.
OL,14,F"It was brutal," Aaron said. "But it's
OL,15,Fmore hindsight now that you realise
OL,16,Fhow brutal it was, because at the
OL,17,Ftime, you're living in the moment and
OL,18,Fyou're just trying to be strong for
OL,19,FSally, and you're trying to be strong
OL,20,Ffor the kids".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772041214
OL,3,CChef to take 'bile duct cancer' fight
OL,4,Cto Westminster after wife's tragic
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FSally passed away just ten months
OL,8,Fafter the cancer was found. Aaron
OL,9,Fbelieves that without that
OL,10,Fcoincidental surgery, the cancer would
OL,11,Fhave remained hidden until it was too
OL,12,Flate. "We would have carried on with
OL,13,Four lives... and then we could have
OL,14,Ffound out when she maybe turned
OL,15,Fyellow. At that point, it's too late".
OL,17,FFollowing the death of Sally, Aaron
OL,18,Fwas left to solo-parent their two
OL,19,Fyoung children, Rex, 7, and Sylvie, 6.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
