FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772041214
OL,3,CChef to take 'bile duct cancer' fight
OL,4,Cto Westminster after wife's tragic
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FCholangiocarcinoma is often referred
OL,8,Fto as a "silent" cancer because its
OL,9,Fsymptoms are frequently missed or
OL,10,Fmisdiagnosed until it is too late for
OL,11,Fcurative surgery.
OL,13,FCommon early symptoms include:
OL,15,FAccording to AMMF, the disease now
OL,16,Faccounts for nearly half of all liver
OL,17,Fcancer cases in England, yet it
OL,18,Fremains significantly under-recognised
OL,19,Fby GPs and hospital doctors.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772041214
OL,3,CChef to take 'bile duct cancer' fight
OL,4,Cto Westminster after wife's tragic
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FOn 25 February, Aaron will meet with
OL,8,FMPs to lobby for better awareness and
OL,9,Fa "rethink" of liver cancer care. He
OL,10,Fhas already shared Sally's story with
OL,11,Fthe NHS to help them learn from her
OL,12,Ftreatment journey.
OL,14,F"I hope that I can mitigate situations
OL,15,Fthat happened with me," Aaron said. "I
OL,16,Fdon't want any family to go through
OL,17,Fwhat I went through".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
