PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772041214
OL,3,CChef to take 'bile duct cancer' fight
OL,4,Cto Westminster after wife's tragic
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FMartha Robinson, from the charity
OL,8,FAMMF, added: "We need faster diagnosis
OL,9,Fand better access to specialists in
OL,10,Fthe NHS. There are an increasing
OL,11,Fnumber of treatments now available
OL,12,Fthat can help extend life
OL,13,Fsignificantly, but we need the health
OL,14,Fservice to help people get the
OL,15,Ftreatment they need"
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,18,FHealth and Social Care was contacted
OL,19,Ffor comment.
OL,26,@pD@NOU
